{"tid":28684,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)索女·喪屍·機關槍 不死殺陣 七俠蕩寇誌","createTime":"2016-12-08T05:52:46.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-08T11:45:02.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"953ed533483083fe998aeddc3659d634e08b5f4d","tid":28684,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T05:52:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour&d=IBnlvbSbe3Blie6hXp8%2BJgT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=020c1e62\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour</a>暫時用住SKLIVE睇先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/e/ee/Planet_Terror_(Netherlands).jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fe%2Fee%2FPlanet_Terror_%28Netherlands%29.jpg&h=b5c4a5e9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://static.srcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/Kurt-Russell-Death-Proof.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.srcdn.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2FKurt-Russell-Death-Proof.jpg&h=aa495d27&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.solarmovie.sc/2016/09/26/poster/69b0c7b199e5eae19068d346217640e4-the-magnificent-seven-1474907919.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.solarmovie.sc%2F2016%2F09%2F26%2Fposter%2F69b0c7b199e5eae19068d346217640e4-the-magnificent-seven-1474907919.jpg&h=b9b03ec6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.脫衣舞女切麗（羅絲&middot;邁格溫飾）邊跳鋼管舞邊流淚，她厭倦並想著逃離這樣的生活，一切爛透了。另一邊，附近軍事基地在研發一種藥物的過程中發生事故，病毒氣體彌漫出來，附近周圍的人們變成了僵屍，而切麗那賴以為生、修長惹火的右腿也被僵屍扯了下來。還好，她身邊還有男友雷（弗萊迪&middot;羅瑞格茲飾）的存在。<br />\n醫院被血洗，員警們無力阻擋僵屍的進攻..<br />\n<br />\n2.麥克(寇特羅素 飾演)以前身分是飛車特技演員，現在則是變態的殺人魔，專挑青春洋溢的年輕女子下手，有著巨大壓迫感的「Death Proof」特技車是他執行瘋狂死刑的神兵利器。不斷犯下重大案件，一州換過一州，直到有天遇上特技同行女車手們，展開彼此旗鼓相當的飛車追殺&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n3.某小鎮長期受到惡勢力集團的霸權欺凌，甚至冷血殘殺。丈夫慘遭毒手的 Emma（希莉賓妮）決定聘請賞金獵人 Sam（丹素華盛頓），為她和其他絕望的鎮民伸張正義，以眼還眼。 Sam 另外找來六名各懷絕技的民間高手，包括賭徒（基斯柏特）、神槍手（伊芬鶴基）、追踪者（雲遜當奴費奧）、刺客（李炳憲）、逃犯（馬尼加斯魯夫）、戰士（馬田沙米亞）合力拯救小鎮。七名俠客迎戰惡霸，誓要推翻橫蠻強權，奪回無價的自由和尊嚴！<br />\n<br />\n2 40PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db518cd6b93815ee30d258920abbba0f2e627641","tid":28684,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T05:56:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef4ce6072928573ea133880a5b79470eaa0c52cc","tid":28684,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T06:29:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98d39b4e0d7967d7c78066a4590170fd04013136","tid":28684,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T06:45:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98bbdd49972e93ced99ad847ef3860f4502bc788","tid":28684,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T07:07:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e93bff1178120446c2c9b81ddfddc448e9ee858","tid":28684,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T07:53:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"572e4ec3ea2b092f19c77a0c370f23b7b1eb3fb6","tid":28684,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:15:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" clas